{"tid":1005994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一帶一路債務陷阱之馬爾代夫","createTime":"2019-02-02T15:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T16:43:39.000Z","uid":234763,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6dd9bb566dee4cc1ed44c94acb03181a68bcce08","tid":1005994,"uid":234763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"美國曾警告一帶一路為受惠國帶來債務陷阱。過程大約係借錢畀窮國，對方無力還款之後就以基建抵債。馬爾代夫就係其中一個受害者，現欠中共30億美元債務，2019至2020要償還15億美元。如無法償還，就以基建股權抵債。換言之，中國會取得馬爾代夫的碼頭公路，控制了該國命脈。更加可以<span style=\"color: red;\">在印度洋建立據點</span>，挑戰區域傳統老大印度。<br />\n<br />\n在眾多基建中，最突出的為<span style=\"color: red;\">中馬友誼大橋</span>，把首都馬累和機場島連在一齊。在中共吹虛之下，成了中國在馬投資的象徵。但其實馬爾代夫只承擔了5-6億人民幣的低息貸款，另外接近一半費用由中國援助，所以可說是中國對馬的援助項目。在30億美元債務中只佔到2-3%，可見中國在當在更多投資。所以將焦點放在中馬友誼大橋上，就捉錯用神。<br />\n<br />\n但馬爾代夫並非一味受中國控制。2018年9月，反對黨勝出大選，新政府批評中國為馬帶來難以償還的債務，嚴查每一單華在當地投資，更單方面<span style=\"color: red;\">取消與中共的自由貿易協議</span>，最後向傳統老大哥印度求助，償還中國債務。現在更指控中國在當地的投資成本過高，懷疑當中金額涉及與前朝前的貪污，要求中國降低債務。<br />\n<br />\n面對強國，馬爾夫代是否能渡過償務危機，我哋拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n中馬友誼大橋行車片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AdSnrGhtyuA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAdSnrGhtyuA&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=928ef9e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AdSnrGhtyuA</a><br />\n參考：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190202/s00014/1549046269158/%E6%96%99%E6%AC%A0%E8%8F%AF200%E5%84%84-%E9%A6%AC%E7%88%BE%E4%BB%A3%E5%A4%AB%E5%80%A1%E6%B8%9B%E5%82%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190202%2Fs00014%2F1549046269158%2F%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E8%258F%25AF200%25E5%2584%2584-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E7%2588%25BE%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2582%25B5&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=1390aa92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190202%2Fs00014%2F1549046269158%2F%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E8%258F%25AF200%25E5%2584%2584-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E7%2588%25BE%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2582%25B5&h=e8c4704b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190202/s00014/1549046269158/%E6%96%99%E6%AC%A0%E8%8F%AF200%E5%84%84-%E9%A6%AC%E7%88%BE%E4%BB%A3%E5%A4%AB%E5%80%A1%E6%B8%9B%E5%82%B5</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/12/17/article/86829/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2018%2F12%2F17%2Farticle%2F86829%2F&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=f2972b1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/12/17/article/86829/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@lineposthk/%E4%BD%99%E9%9D%9E-%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%E9%A6%AC%E7%88%BE%E4%BB%A3%E5%A4%AB%E4%B8%AD%E9%A6%AC%E5%8F%8B%E8%AA%BC%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%AC%8A%E8%A8%80-a52bc02e0825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40lineposthk%2F%25E4%25BD%2599%25E9%259D%259E-%25E6%258A%25B9%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E7%2588%25BE%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%258F%258B%25E8%25AA%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25AC%258A%25E8%25A8%2580-a52bc02e0825&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=921f01c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@lineposthk/%E4%BD%99%E9%9D%9E-%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%E9%A6%AC%E7%88%BE%E4%BB%A3%E5%A4%AB%E4%B8%AD%E9%A6%AC%E5%8F%8B%E8%AA%BC%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%AC%8A%E8%A8%80-a52bc02e0825</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/108641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F108641&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=bb718f90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/108641</a>"},{"pid":"0511bc997